STEP TO INSTALL AND RUN THE PROJECT:

1. Install Python 3.8.5 in the 'Project-code' folder and check the checkbox of 'add-path'and install for 'all users' while installation.
2. Open 'Covid' folder in cmd.
3. Run command 'pip install virtualenv' to install virtualenv for python.
4. Run command 'virtualenv env'.
5. Run command 'env\Scripts\activate' to activate the virtualenv.
6. Run command 'pip install matplotlib'.
7. Run command 'pip install keras'.
8. Run command 'pip install tensorflow'.
9. Run command 'pip install flask'

Please change the path of the data-set in the below files in order to run the code.
change the path to the path of data-set in your system.
ex:, '....../Covid/covid-images' for covid data set.

Please create a folder structure like bellow:
....../Covid/source/test/covid
....../Covid/source/test/normal
....../Covid/source/test/pneumoia
....../Covid/source/train/covid
....../Covid/source/train/normal
....../Covid/source/train/pneumonia
and
....../Covid/downsample/test
....../Covid/downsample/train

10. Run command 'python train-test-split.py'.
11. Run command 'python resize.py'
12. Run command 'python crop.py'.
13. Run command 'python cnn_train.py'.
14. Run command 'python app.py'.
15. After step 9 open browser and open http://localhost:5000/.

Please follow the same order of exicution to face no issues.

Thank you, KARTHIKEYA HS.
